STATE of North Carolina
v.
William Eugene WEBB. No. 608P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 29, 2006. Nora Henry Hargrove, for William Eugene Webb. Amy C. Kunstling, Assistant Attorney General, Rex Gore, District Attorney, Lee Bollinger, Assistant District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 31st day of October 2005 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 29th day of June 2006."
